column232: There are three differrent types of roofs including: overlaid hip, cross hipped, and flat. There have been 3 additions/rennovations since orignial construction. A hipped-roof addition was built onto the back of the fire hall in 1938. Then in 1980 there was an addition connecting the front building to the back building merging them into one unit. Finally, a rennovation and restructure of the roof was completed in 2021 following the damage of the 2020 tornado.
